              },
              "free_text": [
                " EN MEAN = 0.57 MILLI-EV FOR MEASUREMENTS OF",
                " COHERENT SCATTERING LENGTHS AND TOTAL CROSS SECTIONS.",
                " EPITHERMAL NEUTRON EN = 1.26, 5.19 EV SELECTED BY",
