              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".PULVERIZED AND CRYSTALLINE METAL AND TRIOXIDE SAMPLES",
                " WERE USED FOR THE MEASUREMENTS ON NATURAL W.",
                ".THE ENRICHED SAMPLES OF W-182 AND -184 WERE IN",
                " METALLIC FORM, WHILE SAMPLES OF W-183, -184 AND -186",
                " WERE TRIOXIDES.",
                ".THE CHEMICAL PURITY OF ALL THE SAMPLES WAS BETWEEN",
                " 99.51 AND 99.996 PER CENT.",
                ".THE ENRCHED SAMPLES HAD AN ENRICHMENT OF 96.3 TO",
                " 99.44 PER CENT.",
                ".THE OXIDIZED SAMPLES WERE TREATED UNDER ARGON ATMOS-",
                " PHERE."
              ]
            }
